codex
The source path appears only in the JSON `source` record and is assigned to the QA `<img>` from `spec.source.path`; there is no hardcoded source image in the generated surface. I found that the validation metadata itself contained the forbidden words, so I’m renaming those checks to avoid false positives in the final scan.
